and.com/news/healthbeat/coronavirus/friday-covid-19-south-dakota-update-1-more-positive-case/ Noem signs State of Emergency order; Requests schools to close throughout South Dakota next week] [[KELO-TV|KELO]]</ref><ref>[https://siouxcityjournal.com/news/local/state-and-regional/noem-orders-south-dakota-k--schools-to-close-next/article_14ddb2a4-3a5d-5a1c-b467-eb3327f2392e.html Noem orders South Dakota K-12 schools to close next week; Iowa, Nebraska holding off on similar moves] Sioux City Journal</ref>\n__TOC__\n\n== Statistics ==\n{{2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic data/United States/South Dakota medical cases chart}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:right\"\n! colspan=\"4\" |2019 Novel Coronavirus (COVID-19) Cases in South Dakota<ref>{{cite web|url=https://doh.sd.gov/news/Coronavirus.aspx#top |title=Novel Coronavirus (COVID-19) Updates and Information|publisher=South Dakota Department of Health|accessdate=March 17, 2020}}</ref>\nUpdated April 2, 2020 \n|-\n! scope=\"col\" |County\n! scope=\"col\" |Confirmed Cases\n! scope=\"col\" |Recoveries\n! scope=\"col\" |Deaths\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Beadle County, South Dakota|Beadle]]\n|21\n|12\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Bon Homme County, South Dakota|Bon Homme]]\n|1\n|1\n|\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Charles Mix County, South Dakota|Charles Mix]]\n|1\n|1\n|\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Davison County, South Dakota|Davison]]\n|2\n|2\n|1{{efn|Patient was a resident of Pennington County, but died in Davison County.}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[McCook County, South Dakota|McCook]]\n|2\n|1\n|\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Minnehaha County, South Dakota|Minnehaha]]\n|40\n|11\n|\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Brown County, South Dakota|Brown]]\n|4\n|2\n|\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Pennington County, South Dakota|Pennington]]\n|5\n|1\n|\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Brookings County, South Dakota|Brookings]]\n|2\n|2\n|\n|-\n| st